200
00:11:39.378 --> 00:11:42.978
Jadi, pembunuhnya ada di antara orang-orang di sini?

201
00:11:42.978 --> 00:11:46.678
Iya! Sama seperti kau, polisi menunjukkan,

202
00:11:46.678 --> 00:11:48.878
